Package: proton-drive
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsecret-1-0, dbus
Description: Unofficial Proton Drive client for Linux
 Unofficial community client: sync daemon, CLI, and graphical interface.
 Syncs files between your local machine and Proton Drive.
 .
 This package is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Proton AG.
 .
 This package provides:
  - protond: the sync daemon (systemd user service)
  - proton-drive: command-line interface
  - proton-gui: graphical user interface
 .
 Man pages are installed for proton-drive(1) and protond(1).
